{"tid":238131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講到咁大愛世人，叫你地實際行動捐錢又咪屌曬鬼","createTime":"2017-05-10T23:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T10:22:43.000Z","uid":33481,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"255920ff00375a9305d4e9ab15aa708012db71f4","tid":238131,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:05:00.000Z","msg":"口講支持條女就叻，一叫你捐錢就口爽荷包立，作幾萬個籍口反捐錢，話條女唔需要錢有、話捐錢當姐係當條女係雞又有、話會有社工跟進所以唔洗捐又有、話條女未必有ptsd所以唔洗錢醫又有、人身攻擊又有。<br />\n<br />\n緊係啦，一捐錢犯到自己本喎，唔捐又會俾人發現自己得把口只係想拎道德高地唔想付出，真係人生兩難式呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65644c5ba55ef4908608f0628c4b24928388de7c","tid":238131,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:05:44.000Z","msg":"連登仔最叻咪......"},{"pid":"6cc4672a35b5e678eb3a9e706d553674676a99ae","tid":238131,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔最叻咪......</blockquote><br />\n我就唔會好似佢地咁企道德高地，我擺明人渣黎既，條女係生係死唔關我事，捐錢呢d係享受左道德高地既大愛撚應有既責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da846c015b1bb6431164177c7d47924b54069c8","tid":238131,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:10:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30a4a476d4d2540b1373112560dbc5b77e431f01","tid":238131,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:11:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f8735af5277b792fc33e41cf24f4f948ee68435","tid":238131,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連香港人係咁，口裏說道德，身體最誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n口裡說道德<br />\n身體很誠實<br />\n<br />\n呢句高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3cf565411df67fbb907a17ba7ed012c9a290fc","tid":238131,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:13:32.000Z","ms